properties.characteristics: Largest order of non-stromatic discomycetes, usually have brightly coloured apothecia, distinguished by disc or cup-shaped apothecia, live as saprobes on organic matter.
properties.name: Helotiales
Monilinia fructicola
properties.description: Causal agent of brown rot of stone fruits.
